Description: Local AI inference with Ollama
 SecuBox module for managing local LLM inference via Ollama.
 Provides container management (Docker/Podman), model pulling,
 chat completion, and text generation APIs.
 .
 Ported from OpenWRT luci-app-ollama.
 Provides FastAPI backend on /api/v1/ollama/ via Unix socket.
